bodyText: Dear Acme Corporation, This is a friendly reminder about your outstanding balance. Please arrange payment at your earliest convenience.
Welcome to our collection process. Please review the attached statement.
Called accounts payable department. Left voicemail regarding overdue invoices.
Second notice regarding outstanding invoices. Please contact us to discuss payment.
FINAL NOTICE BEFORE LEGAL ACTION: Legal proceedings will commence within 7 business days if payment is not received.
Spoke with CFO regarding payment plan options. Customer requested extension which was denied.
Thank you for your payment. Your account is now current. We appreciate your business.
Payment reminder for outstanding invoices. Please process payment or contact us.
ESCALATION NOTICE: Your account has been escalated due to non-payment.
Following up on our previous communication. Please review attached statement.
Your account requires immediate attention. Payment is now over 60 days past due.
